# CLAUDE.local.md — Personal preferences (not checked into git)
# Copy this to CLAUDE.local.md and customize.

## My Preferences
- I prefer TypeScript over JavaScript
- Use functional components, not class components
- I like concise commit messages
- When in doubt, ask me — don't guess

## My Shortcuts
- "ship it" = commit + push + create PR
- "lgtm" = approved, proceed to next phase
- "nuke it" = discard current approach, start fresh
